The '''Sicilian Wikipedia''' ({{lang-scn|Wikipedia ’n sicilianu}}) is the [[Sicilian language|Sicilian-language]] edition of the free online encyclopedia [[Wikipedia]]. It was created on 5 October 2004.<ref>[http://stats.wikimedia.org/EN/TablesWikipediaSCN.htm SCN.wiki]</ref>
As of {{CURRENTMONTHNAME}} {{CURRENTYEAR}} it contains more than {{NUMBEROF|ARTICLES|scn|N}} articles.

